==Galician==
===Alternative forms===
* {{l|gl|xograr}}
===Etymology===
From Old Galician and {{inh|gl|roa-opt|jograr}} (13th century, ''{{w|Cantigas de Santa Maria}}''), ultimately from {{der|gl|la|ioculāris|t=jocular, laughable}}. Cognate with {{cog|pt|jogral}} and {{cog|gl|juglar}}.
===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|gl|/ʃoˈɣɾal/}}
